; Regression test: use-after-free when a transaction with a deferred
; posting is rejected during finalization.
;
; A transaction containing a deferred posting (<Account>) and a virtual
; posting with no amount causes finalize() to throw balance_error.
; The destructor frees the deferred posting but did not remove it from
; the account's deferred_posts map, leaving a dangling pointer that
; apply_deferred_posts() later dereferenced.
;
; Before the fix, this crashed with SIGSEGV (exit 139).
; After the fix, it exits cleanly with a parse error (exit 1).

2024/01/01 Trigger Transaction
    ; UUID: poc-uuid-0001
    <Assets:Checking>      $100
    Expenses:Food
    (Misc)

2024/01/01 Second Transaction
    ; UUID: poc-uuid-0001
    <Assets:Checking>      $50
    Income               $-50

test bal
__ERROR__
While parsing file "$FILE", line 5:
Error: There cannot be null amounts after balancing a transaction
end test